### Create a new transaction (Transfer)
POST http://localhost:3000/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fromAccount": "ACC-12345",
  "toAccount": "ACC-67890",
  "amount": 555.50,
  "currency": "USD",
  "type": "transfer"
}

###

### Get all transactions
GET http://localhost:3000/transactions

###

### Filter transactions by accountId
GET http://localhost:3000/transactions?accountId=ACC-12345

###

### Filter transactions by type
GET http://localhost:3000/transactions?type=transfer

###

### Filter transactions by date range
GET http://localhost:3000/transactions?from=2026-01-01&to=2026-01-31

###

### Combine multiple filters (accountId + type)
GET http://localhost:3000/transactions?accountId=ACC-12345&type=deposit

###

### Combine multiple filters (accountId + date range)
GET http://localhost:3000/transactions?accountId=ACC-12345&from=2026-01-24

###

### Get a specific transaction by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/transactions/{{transactionId}}

###

